Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed across all variants where both activities occur
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time it takes from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation until SW-Reviewer Agreed is performed in cases that follow the variant ending with SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average cycle time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation when followed by SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion versus when followed directly by Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time elapsed between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants involving multiple reviewer declines or unavailability events
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in processes that eventually reach SW-Reviewer Agreed after at least one Reviewer Invitation Reminder
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed in the longest-performing variant (performance = 47316796.000)
Metric: the minimum of the function base == 47316796.000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Agreed compared to the time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Elapsed time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed in cases that include Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Reviewer Agreed after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in variants that include Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in traces where SW-Reviewer Agreed eventually occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Agreed in cases requiring Assign a Different Editor intervention
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed to occur after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation in variants that do not include any reminder activities (Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 or 2)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed in comparison with the time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'
